OL,3,COusted Bangladeshi PM indicted for
OL,4,Ccrimes against humanity
OL,6,FA special tribunal on Thursday
OL,7,Findicted Bangladesh's ousted Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sheikh Hasina by accepting
OL,9,Fcharges of crimes against humanity,
OL,10,Ffiled against her in connection with a
OL,11,Fmass uprising in which hundreds of
OL,12,Fstudents were killed last year.
OL,14,FA three-member panel, headed by
OL,15,FJustice Golam Mortuza Mozumder,
OL,16,Findicted Hasina, former Home Minister
OL,17,FAsaduzzaman Khan and former police
OL,18,Fchief Chowdhury Abdullah Al-Mamun on
OL,19,Ffive charges.
