OL,4,Ccrimes against humanity
OL,6,FHasina and Khan are being tried in
OL,7,Fabsentia.
OL,9,FHasina - who ruled Bangladesh for 15
OL,10,Fyears - fled the country in August
OL,11,F2024, following weeks of anti-
OL,12,Fgovernment protests which culminated
OL,13,Fwith demonstrators entering her
OL,14,Fofficial residence.
