OL,6,FThe protests began over a quota system
OL,7,Fthat reserved 30% of government jobs
OL,8,Ffor the families of veterans who
OL,9,Ffought in Bangladesh's war of
OL,10,Findependence against Pakistan in 1971.
OL,12,FThe country now has an interim
OL,13,Fgovernment, led by Nobel Peace Prize
OL,14,Flaureate Muhammad Yunus.
