OL,3,COusted Bangladeshi PM indicted for
OL,4,Ccrimes against humanity
OL,6,FThe tribunal, which opened the trial
OL,7,Fon June 5, had asked Hasina to appear
OL,8,Fbefore it. Authorities published
OL,9,Fnewspaper advertisements asking
OL,10,FHasina, who has been in exile in
OL,11,FIndia, and Khan to appear before the
OL,12,Ftribunal.
OL,14,FBangladesh's interim government sent a
OL,15,Fformal request to India for Hasina's
OL,16,Fextradition, but India has not
OL,17,Fresponded.
