OL,3,COusted Bangladeshi PM indicted for
OL,4,Ccrimes against humanity
OL,6,FKhan is possibly also in India. Al-
OL,7,FMamun was arrested and was in the dock
OL,8,Fon Thursday while the judges indicted
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, Al-Mamun pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fand told the tribunal that he would
OL,13,Fmake a statement in favor of the
OL,14,Fprosecution at a later stage. The
OL,15,Fprosecution offered a leaked audio of
OL,16,FHasina and other documents as evidence
OL,17,Fto the tribunal.
